<TEXT>
<P>
We also checked on "The Punisher" -- with Dolph Lundgren as Marvel comics' 
lean, mean vigilante -- once set for release early last year, then shelved with 
the sale of New World. 
</P>
<P>
New World has since distributed it internationally throughout most of Europe 
and the Far East. It opens next month in Australia -- and is currently being 
shopped to domestic distributors. Pat H. Broeske 
</P>
