<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEW HOMES ON VIEW 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Los Angeles County 
</P>
<P>
PASADENA: Victorian Courts, 7 2-3 bedroom condominiums; 1,140-1,260 square 
feet; $175,000-$195,000; features include fireplaces, balconies, individual 
alarm systems and deluxe kitchens; builder, Tag Development Co.; $105-$110 
monthly association dues; close of escrow move-ins; open Saturday and Sunday 10 
a.m.-5 p.m. at 29 S. Allen Ave., reached from the southbound Allen Avenue exit 
of the Foothill (210) Freeway. 
</P>
<P>
SAN DIMAS: Final phase of Palazzo di Via Verde, 6 of 24 4-6 bedroom 
