Schloss Durnstein: A-3601, Durnstein, Austria, Europe; summer rates about $75 
to $120 per person a night, breakfast included. 
</P>
<P>
Murren, Hohfluh and Meiringen, Switzerland: Swiss National Tourist Office, 222 
N. Sepulveda Blvd., Suite 1570, El Segundo 90245; (213) 335-5980. 
</P>
<P>
Portofino, Italy: Italian Government Travel Office, 360 Post St., Suite 801, 
San Francisco 94108; (415) 392-6206, call before 1 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
Puerto Vallarta, Mexico: Mexican Government Tourism Office, 10100 Santa Monica 
Blvd., Suite 224, Los Angeles 90067; (213) 203-8191 or (800) 262-8900. 
</P>
