<HEADLINE>
<P>
TRIVIA CORRECTIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As a teacher of geography and an airline buff, I was disappointed to find 
several glaring errors in the "Can You Guess?" trivia quiz. They are: 1) The 
airline of Spain is IBERIA not Iberian; 2) it's Qantas not Quantas; 3) LACSA 
not LASCA (Lineas Aereas Costarricenses S.A.) and 4) Colombia not Columbia. 
</P>
<P>
FRANK S. BROWNIE 
</P>
<P>
Santa Barbara 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
