<HEADLINE>
<P>
SUPREME COURT UPHOLDS STAY OF EXECUTION FOR HARRIS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The trial, 12 years of appeals and the reprieve of Harris' death sentence could 
have all been avoided had he seen fit to give the two teen-agers a last-minute 
reprieve. 
</P>
<P>
What a shame. 
</P>
<P>
ANITA M. WARFEL 
</P>
<P>
Rancho Dominguez 
</P>
