contest, a celebrity car race and a chili cook-off will be featured at the 
ninth annual Beachfest, presented by Beach Charities. Shoreline Aquatic Park, 
Pine Avenue and Shoreline Drive, Long Beach, 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. today. 
</P>
