<HEADLINE>
<P>
ALLEGED SPEED TRAP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I read with great disgust your article (March 31) regarding the attorney, 
Ernest J. Franceshi Jr., wanting to sue my city because of an alleged speed 
trap. 
</P>
<P>
Poor guy! Eighty-five m.p.h. in a 55-m.p.h. zone; 75 m.p.h. in a 55-m.p.h. 
zone; and 70 m.p.h. in a 50-m.p.h. zone. Next thing he'll want is that if he is 
the cause of an accident going that fast, he'll be suing for not having an 
officer there to stop him. It's a shame he doesn't use his legal talents for 
something more productive. 
</P>
<P>
GARY ARNESON 
</P>
<P>
Huntington Beach 
</P>
