</P>
<P>
He also confirmed his attendance for the April 3 forum sponsored by the Tustin 
Meadows Community Assn. The confirmation was made to their management company. 
On April 2, at the Tustin City Council Meeting when Kelly was confronted with 
some alleged actions involving misuse of his position, he struck back with a 
comment that he would be at the Tustin Meadows forum the following night and he 
could be asked those questions there. Again he didn't show! 
</P>
