<HEADLINE>
<P>
WATER WASTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Did anyone notice the two photos on Page B3 (April 4) of water gushing from 
hoses, which were captioned "Stadium Gussied Up for Home Opener?" And on Page 
B6 was an editorial "Why Gamble With Our Water," in which we were wisely 
advised to make some minor sacrifices to conserve the water supply. 
</P>
<P>
I laughed so hard, I went out and "gussied up" my petunias. 
</P>
<P>
JUNE HUFF 
</P>
<P>
Carlsbad 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
