<HEADLINE>
<P>
WATCH THAT COUNCIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I would like to congratulate you on your new Ventura County section. I 
delivered The Times as a boy and have been a faithful reader since that time. 
</P>
<P>
Now I have one small request. Please expand your coverage of the Ventura City 
Council. This group bears watching, as I noted in your article "Vote Delayed on 
Ban of Big Boats in Yards." This ordinance was brought up without a public 
hearing, and when I called this morning, they had no plans for a public 
hearing. This affects me directly, as I just installed 90 feet of driveway and 
a 12-by-30-foot pad to store my boat in the back yard. 
</P>
<P>
The press is my only link to city government, and I can't emphasize how 
important that link can be. 
</P>
<P>
WYLEE D. McCRARY 
</P>
<P>
Ventura 
</P>
