<P>
RICK SCHU 
</P>
<P>
Age: 28 
</P>
<P>
Position: Infielder 
</P>
<P>
Major league experience: Four years, 162 days 
</P>
<P>
How obtained: Signed as free agent, Feb. 10, 1990. 
</P>
<P>
Pertinent stats: Spent most of last season with Detroit, with 7 home runs and 
21 RBIs in 98 games. 
</P>
<P>
Comments: Right-handed hitter who once was tabbed as the replacement for 
Philadelphia third baseman Mike Schmidt. Can play third base, outfield and has 
been working out as a catcher. Schu does not hit for power, but is considered a 
good contact hitter. 
</P>
